* <SIGNATURE>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | Instance Public Method /SCMTMS/CL_DAM_UH_LDA_TORFU_AI->GET_SELECT_OPTIONS
* +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | [<---] ET_SELOPT                      TYPE        /BOBF/T_FRW_QUERY_SELPARAM
* +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</SIGNATURE>
  method GET_SELECT_OPTIONS.
  SET EXTENDED CHECK OFF.

  DATA: ls_selopt TYPE /BOBF/S_FRW_QUERY_SELPARAM.

  /SCMTMS/IF_SRVMGR_MOCK~MV_OWN_LOGSYS = 'ER9CLNT815' .

  CLEAR et_selopt.

  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_cust'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = ''.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_table'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = '/SCMTMS/C_*'.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_tattr'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = ''.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_noclnt'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = 'X'.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_smgr'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = ''.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_dac'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = 'X'.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_bo'.
  ls_selopt-sign           = 'I'.
  ls_selopt-option         = 'EQ'.
  ls_selopt-low            = '/SCMTMS/TOR'.
  APPEND ls_selopt TO et_selopt.
  CLEAR ls_selopt.
  ls_selopt-attribute_name = 'p_qid'.
